[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/07/92/79290.jpg","floor":"#2","id":"1336194","time":"2018-4-11 01:26","userId":"continuer","userName":"Euphy","userSign":"(ユーフェミア·リ·ブリタニア/Euphemia Li Britannia ...)","message":"我已经忘光了 <br>ps.除了书剑恩仇录其他都读过","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/19/211998.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1336195","time":"2018-4-11 01:34","userId":"211998","userName":"秘则为花","userSign":"(人啊，你曾经作为人活过吗？)","message":"夜半砌墙b38<br><span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">就是感觉结局比较草率的，一方面不想让狄云杀人，一方面又想制裁坏人，最后弄了一个钱里有毒，仿佛是相信天意昭昭，多行不义，老天自会出手，有些消极。不看作者，倒认不出是金庸的作品</span>","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#3-1","id":"1336200","time":"2018-4-11 01:59","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"<span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">确实不像金庸的作品，给人的感觉过于畸形了，哪怕是欧阳锋金轮法王这种只差把反派写在脸上的角色，也没有被刻画得这么畸形过。欧阳锋好歹还把欧阳克视若己出，金轮法王还能为了救郭襄拼命，连城诀里面除了丁典等两三个人物以外，不论正邪几乎所有人都没有人味，晚上看得人发怵</span>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/19/211931.jpg","floor":"#3-2","id":"1336227","time":"2018-4-11 07:10","userId":"dhzy","userName":"dhzy","userSign":"","message":"突然全死了，感觉是个闹剧<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/34/3417.jpg","floor":"#3-3","id":"1336237","time":"2018-4-11 08:07","userId":"venusxx","userName":"Venusxx","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">dhzy</span> 说: 突然全死了，感觉是个闹剧<br>//</q></div>不信抬头看，苍天放过谁<br><br>最后金老师是编不下去了"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/19/211931.jpg","floor":"#4","id":"1336199","time":"2018-4-11 01:58","userId":"dhzy","userName":"dhzy","userSign":"","message":"这部东西比较理想化所以给人感觉不是那么真实。<br>里面到处是坏人。一般我们说一个人是坏人是幼稚的讲法，因为人是多面而立体的。但是连城诀里的诸位...坏得彻底，黑得透亮，不是因为遇到什么变故而黑化<span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">慕容复</span>，是从里到外纯粹的恶人，是从头到脚毫无可爱之处的恶人<span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">南海鳄神</span>。这么短的篇幅塞进去这么多恶心角色，酿成一盆名副其实不含杂质的屎，我怀疑作者就是奔着屎能有多臭的心态来试验创作的。<br>结局没有全灭还行。<br>神他妈半夜砌墙。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#4-1","id":"1336201","time":"2018-4-11 02:01","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"对，几乎所有角色都是一开始就是纯粹的坏，看得人难受至极<br><span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">你看林平之和万圭都是杀妻，但是林出场的时候还是很富有正义感的公子哥，经历了家破人亡等种种变故之后才变得偏激，最后癫狂之下杀了小师妹。万圭呢？他不需要理由</span><br>当然和你说得一样这个东西很理想，不真实或者说很极端，不过单就从\"让人难受\"这一点上来说我觉得比很多死了主要角色或者就是单纯让人全灭的作品来说效果真的是要好得多了<br><span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">半夜砌墙是真的吓人</span>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/19/211931.jpg","floor":"#4-2","id":"1336228","time":"2018-4-11 07:10","userId":"dhzy","userName":"dhzy","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">akito_sakurai</span> 说: 对，几乎所有角色都是一开始就是纯粹的坏，看得人难受至极<br>你看林平之和万圭都是杀妻，但是林出场的时候还是很富有正义感的公子哥，经历了家破人亡等种种变故之后才变得偏激，最后癫狂之下杀了小师妹。万圭呢？他不...</q></div>半夜看这个辛苦了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/76/297631.jpg","floor":"#4-3","id":"1336283","time":"2018-4-11 10:48","userId":"ydc123","userName":"ydc","userSign":"","message":"花铁干不服？"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/19/211931.jpg","floor":"#4-4","id":"1336299","time":"2018-4-11 11:17","userId":"dhzy","userName":"dhzy","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">ydc</span> 说: 花铁干不服？</q></div>从他轻易投降那里我就觉得这人本来就不配大侠之名了"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/76/297631.jpg","floor":"#4-5","id":"1336300","time":"2018-4-11 11:20","userId":"ydc123","userName":"ydc","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">dhzy</span> 说: 从他轻易投降那里我就觉得这人本来就不配大侠之名了</q></div>轻易投降那一刻就是人生转折点啊<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/19/211931.jpg","floor":"#4-6","id":"1336302","time":"2018-4-11 11:27","userId":"dhzy","userName":"dhzy","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">ydc</span> 说: 轻易投降那一刻就是人生转折点啊</q></div>从那以后就抛弃了大侠的负担开始放飞自我~~~"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/42/14268.jpg","floor":"#5","id":"1336204","time":"2018-4-11 02:24","userId":"calfn","userName":"触触✅个人认证","userSign":"","message":"聊这个跟能促进婚恋育儿吗∑(´△｀)？！","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#5-1","id":"1336207","time":"2018-4-11 02:28","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"不能，能传播负能量<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/42/14268.jpg","floor":"#5-2","id":"1336281","time":"2018-4-11 10:37","userId":"calfn","userName":"触触✅个人认证","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">akito_sakurai</span> 说: 不能，能传播负能量</q></div>如果大家都看，高达和驾驶员都看，那就没什么好搞了吧"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#5-3","id":"1336293","time":"2018-4-11 11:07","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">柳胜薰CALFN-触触SVIP</span> 说: 如果大家都看，高达和驾驶员都看，那就没什么好搞了吧</q></div>高达不会对这种东西感兴趣的吧"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/01/42/14268.jpg","floor":"#5-4","id":"1336298","time":"2018-4-11 11:11","userId":"calfn","userName":"触触✅个人认证","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">akito_sakurai</span> 说: 高达不会对这种东西感兴趣的吧</q></div>bgm高达的境界有点高"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/icon.jpg","floor":"#6","id":"1336206","time":"2018-4-11 02:27","userId":"372144","userName":"霞ヶ丘先生@いい笑颜でした","userSign":"(合縁奇縁，一期一会，袖すり合うも多生の縁。 ...)","message":"已经忘光了，只记得一些关键词……毕竟在我印象中这部作品不是很出彩。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#7","id":"1336208","time":"2018-4-11 02:35","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"(明天的事，都不一定知道，未来的事情，怎么能知道呢？ ... ... ...)","message":"说起来我小时候好像看过连城诀的电视剧，虽然完全不记得剧情了。看过小说回头来看是真的想不通为什么会有人想到把这种小说改编成电视剧的……","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/31/34/313469.jpg","floor":"#8","id":"1336212","time":"2018-4-11 03:39","userId":"313469","userName":"Cedar","userSign":"(｡´-д-)","message":"之前看过..(唯一看过的金庸小说..因为短..)受人推荐看的..当时还以为是正统武侠..直到主角第一次被坑时开始意识到不对劲..然后留了个心眼..之后剧情就没有太多出意料的地方了..反而读着读着读出了套路感..每当感觉某个家伙将来会使坏时他将来就真的使坏了之类的..刚读完后要是让我评价每个人物我都有很多话想说(现在连出场人物有谁都差不多忘光了..就记得个\"哥翁喊上来\"<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">) 但情绪上其实没有太多起伏..或许是性格使然? 总之要是遇到那些更立体的角色可能我的印象反而会更深一些..","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/icon.jpg","floor":"#9","id":"1336216","time":"2018-4-11 05:19","userId":"262593","userName":"kankanzaishuo","userSign":"(我为歌狂什么时候能发原声碟和办主题音乐会啊…… ...)","message":"很重口的武侠小说，当时看的时候前两回就被唬住了，什么打得皮开肉绽，穿骨，泼尿，后面还有食人，断肢，大出血，当然还有金老爷子的拿手活：牛头人……","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/65/216553.jpg","floor":"#10","id":"1336223","time":"2018-4-11 06:23","userId":"216553","userName":"红楼白衣","userSign":"(吹黑自重)","message":"有件乌蚕衣是多么的重要","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/19/211931.jpg","floor":"#10-1","id":"1336229","time":"2018-4-11 07:20","userId":"dhzy","userName":"dhzy","userSign":"","message":"防+999"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/26/41/264146.jpg","floor":"#11","id":"1336226","time":"2018-4-11 07:09","userId":"264146","userName":"小T","userSign":"(愿意给我5分钟的编辑时间吗？)","message":"作为金庸全集都读过（好像？）的书迷，个人还挺喜欢这部的，大概和丁典在狱中那段还蛮有趣的关系......","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/19/211931.jpg","floor":"#11-1","id":"1336230","time":"2018-4-11 07:23","userId":"dhzy","userName":"dhzy","userSign":"","message":"哪里有趣<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/36/06/360675.jpg","floor":"#11-2","id":"1336238","time":"2018-4-11 08:07","userId":"blackadder","userName":"Blackadder","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">dhzy</span> 说: 哪里有趣</q></div>有点像唐泰斯遇到神甫，这种在低谷期遇到人生导师式角色的故事本身挺吸引人。<br>而且大故事套小故事，丁典的爱情故事非常凄惨魔幻，读罢很长一段时间都记忆犹新..."},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/34/3417.jpg","floor":"#11-3","id":"1336239","time":"2018-4-11 08:08","userId":"venusxx","userName":"Venusxx","userSign":"","message":"来说说"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#11-4","id":"1336240","time":"2018-4-11 08:16","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Blackadder</span> 说: 有点像唐泰斯遇到神甫，这种在低谷期遇到人生导师式角色的故事本身挺吸引人。<br>而且大故事套小故事，丁典的爱情故事非常凄惨魔幻，读罢很长一段时间都记忆犹新...</q></div>丁典的爱情大概是全书唯一值得信赖的关系了，简直是对故事和主角的一种救赎<span style=\"background-color:#555;color:#555;border:1px solid #555;\">然而这种救赎属于两个死去的角色，这一点上又显得特别残忍和讽刺</span>"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/19/211931.jpg","floor":"#11-5","id":"1336262","time":"2018-4-11 09:56","userId":"dhzy","userName":"dhzy","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Blackadder</span> 说: 有点像唐泰斯遇到神甫，这种在低谷期遇到人生导师式角色的故事本身挺吸引人。<br>而且大故事套小故事，丁典的爱情故事非常凄惨魔幻，读罢很长一段时间都记忆犹新...</q></div>据说就是参考那本写的"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/30/78/307891.jpg","floor":"#12","id":"1336241","time":"2018-4-11 08:19","userId":"307891","userName":"川水","userSign":"(Anime is a gag, and so are its dilettantes.)","message":"毕竟是基督山伯爵改的，本身就极端的作品想写的有区别再有点突破，就只能更极端的。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/30/343003.jpg","floor":"#13","id":"1336251","time":"2018-4-11 09:07","userId":"yushenjushi","userName":"Leonhard Euler","userSign":"(沿着公式就能通向真理。)","message":"我很喜欢这部小说，在我心中地位仅次于天龙和笑傲。（金老的书上联鹿没读过，下联读过笑，神，倚）<br>很极端的小说，然而花铁生告诉你人是怎么变坏的。何况有的时候人就是这么坏，小说不过是单单抽出这一面放大了而已。而丁典和凌霜华的爱情，在此衬托下格外凄美。血刀老祖这个纯粹的恶棍也让我印象深刻。<br>至于结局，还好吧，狄云本来就是非常弱势一直都是被推着走的人，不然要怎么办。<br>末尾我看得很感慨，水笙之于狄云虽然不是挚爱，但对彼此来说，对方都是唯一的救赎吧，无尽的黑暗里透出了一点阳光，超级温暖。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/76/297631.jpg","floor":"#13-1","id":"1336284","time":"2018-4-11 10:48","userId":"ydc123","userName":"ydc","userSign":"","message":"花铁干<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">，同喜欢连城诀"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/19/211931.jpg","floor":"#13-2","id":"1336292","time":"2018-4-11 11:02","userId":"dhzy","userName":"dhzy","userSign":"","message":"史铁干<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/34/30/343003.jpg","floor":"#13-3","id":"1336311","time":"2018-4-11 12:37","userId":"yushenjushi","userName":"Leonhard Euler","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">ydc</span> 说: 花铁干，同喜欢连城诀</q></div>手残了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/23/32/233234.jpg","floor":"#14","id":"1336252","time":"2018-4-11 09:07","userId":"porepoem","userName":"porepoem","userSign":"(是动画片儿不是动漫)","message":"一开始没想起是啥，看了看楼上，突然意识到小时候看过电视剧……你让我回想起了一个童年阴影<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br>说来也怪，我连看过这部电视剧都刚刚才想起来，却能清楚的记得主人公的长相，可以说是非常深刻了","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#14-1","id":"1336273","time":"2018-4-11 10:12","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"什么阴影，半夜砌墙吗<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/23/32/233234.jpg","floor":"#14-2","id":"1336274","time":"2018-4-11 10:19","userId":"porepoem","userName":"porepoem","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">akito_sakurai</span> 说: 什么阴影，半夜砌墙吗</q></div>半夜砌墙是什么我忘了，影响最深刻的是落花流水四大侠葫芦娃救爷爷(一个比一个死得惨)，然后那个姓花的(好像是？)食人<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#14-3","id":"1336276","time":"2018-4-11 10:22","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">porepoem</span> 说: 半夜砌墙是什么我忘了，影响最深刻的是落花流水四大侠葫芦娃救爷爷，然后那个姓花的(好像是？)食人</q></div>食人在电视剧里也拍了吗，我以为这种肯定要删掉的……"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/23/32/233234.jpg","floor":"#14-4","id":"1336280","time":"2018-4-11 10:33","userId":"porepoem","userName":"porepoem","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">akito_sakurai</span> 说: 食人在电视剧里也拍了吗，我以为这种肯定要删掉的……</q></div>真拍了……隐约记得还拍的挺真实(没看过小说，不过电视剧雪山上那一段剧情给我的感觉是都很真实，应该是该有的不该有的都拍出来了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">)，现在想起来当时的审核机制着实让人猜不透"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/76/297631.jpg","floor":"#14-5","id":"1336286","time":"2018-4-11 10:52","userId":"ydc123","userName":"ydc","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">akito_sakurai</span> 说: 食人在电视剧里也拍了吗，我以为这种肯定要删掉的……</q></div>真拍了，花铁干是六小龄童演的。不过电视剧里让花铁干给观众狂攒了一波怒气后，就让狄云在众目睽睽之下揭穿并打死了花铁干"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#14-6","id":"1336287","time":"2018-4-11 10:55","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">ydc</span> 说: 真拍了，花铁干是六小龄童演的。不过电视剧里让花铁干给观众狂攒了一波怒气后，就让狄云在众目睽睽之下揭穿并打死了花铁干</q></div>这么说前面的掉头断腿也都拍了？<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/29/76/297631.jpg","floor":"#14-7","id":"1336288","time":"2018-4-11 10:56","userId":"ydc123","userName":"ydc","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">akito_sakurai</span> 说: 这么说前面的掉头断腿也都拍了？</q></div>应该是拍了的，不过再细节的就想不起来了，毕竟是小学看的"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/23/32/233234.jpg","floor":"#14-8","id":"1336296","time":"2018-4-11 11:08","userId":"porepoem","userName":"porepoem","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">akito_sakurai</span> 说: 这么说前面的掉头断腿也都拍了？</q></div>这个有……印象深刻<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">当时我还是个孩子"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/24/87/248715.jpg","floor":"#14-9","id":"1336297","time":"2018-4-11 11:11","userId":"akito_sakurai","userName":"akito_sakurai","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">porepoem</span> 说: 这个有……印象深刻当时我还是个孩子</q></div>以前真是开放，放现在估计都和谐了"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/13/35/133586.jpg","floor":"#15","id":"1336285","time":"2018-4-11 10:50","userId":"shahem","userName":"Shahem","userSign":"(Are you OK?)","message":"前半部疑云漫天，后半部惨象遍地。——孔庆东","sub":[]}]